                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Leishman</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-08-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 13, 1904</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hay instructs Mr. Leishman to accept the note of the minister for foreign
                    affairs of the 12th instant as a compliance with our claims, to insist upon
                    acceptance of the views of the United States Government of its rights in the
                    case, to remain at his post until further advised, and to direct the fleet to
                    withdraw at once.)</p>
            </div>
